android.car.diagnostic

类 CarDiagnosticEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.diagnostic.CarDiagnosticEvent

  • public final class CarDiagnosticEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    A CarDiagnosticEvent object corresponds to a single diagnostic event frame coming from the car.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.Builder
      This class can be used to incrementally construct a CarDiagnosticEvent.
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.CommonIgnitionMonitors
      Contains information about ignition monitors common to all vehicle types.
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.CompressionIgnitionMonitors
      Contains information about ignition monitors specific to compression vehicles.
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.FuelSystemStatus
      Represents possible states of the fuel system; see IntegerSensorIndex.FUEL_SYSTEM_STATUS
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.FuelType
      Represents possible types of fuel; see IntegerSensorIndex.FUEL_TYPE
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.IgnitionMonitor
      Represents the state of an ignition monitor on a vehicle.
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.SecondaryAirStatus
      Represents possible states of the secondary air system; see IntegerSensorIndex.COMMANDED_SECONDARY_AIR_STATUS
      static class  CarDiagnosticEvent.SparkIgnitionMonitors
      Contains information about ignition monitors specific to spark vehicles.

    • 字段详细资料

      • frameType

        public final int frameType
        Whether this frame represents a live or a freeze frame

      • timestamp

        public final long timestamp
        When this data was acquired in car or received from car. It is elapsed real-time of data reception from car in nanoseconds since system boot.

      • dtc

        public final java.lang.String dtc
        Diagnostic Troubleshooting Code (DTC) that was detected and caused this frame to be stored (if a freeze frame). Always null for a live frame.

        public static final <any> CREATOR

      • writeToJson

        public void writeToJson(JsonWriter jsonWriter)
                 throws java.io.IOException
        Store the contents of this diagnostic event in a JsonWriter. The data is stored as a JSON object, with these fields: type: either "live" or "freeze" depending on the type of frame; timestamp: the timestamp at which this frame was generated; intValues: an array of objects each of which has two elements: id: the integer identifier of the sensor; value: the integer value of the sensor; floatValues: an array of objects each of which has two elements: id: the integer identifier of the sensor; value: the floating-point value of the sensor; stringValue: the DTC for a freeze frame, omitted for a live frame
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException
